    "body": "ok, figured it out,\r\nthis is a limitation of `ecryptfs`, filenames cannot be longer than 140 characters, instead of the normal 255, as some information is appended for encryption purpose. \r\n\r\nRelated status-go issue https://github.com/status-im/status-go/issues/2027",
